Dear Richard,

Walkers (Cayman counsel/administrator) has confirmed that the self-certific=
ation form and KYC material for Mrs. Tamar Marash are all in good order. Ad=
ditionally, Cadwalader (Issuer counsel) has confirmed that the purchase agr=
eement is also in good order. Thank you again for your help.

With regards to blanks in the purchase agreement around the date for the pr=
e-pricing offering memorandum and the pricing date, Cadwalader will insert =
them once confirmed, and will send you the updated purchase agreement and r=
equest your confirmation that you release the signature from escrow. We wou=
ld then expect Mrs. Tamar Marash to fund the day after pricing. We expect t=
o distribute the pre-pricing offering memorandum on Friday, September 18 an=
d pricing date is expected to be next week Tuesday, September 22, with fund=
ing by Wednesday September 23 at the latest as per the instructions in the =
purchase agreement. We will keep you posted.

Please let us know if you have any questions.

Thank you & kind regards,
Mehmet

Mehmet Tuncer
Coller Capital
